# Dev Login

Admin login: `http://localhost:8000/auth/admin-login/`

| Email | Password | Role |
|-------|----------|------|
| `admin@email.com` | `123` | admin |

Reset admin password if needed:

```bash
python -c "import django,os;os.environ['DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE']='backend.settings';django.setup();from core.models import User;u=User.objects.filter(role='admin').first();u.set_password('123');u.save();print('done')"
```
